//hkfactcheck.io/crashes/1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhkfactcheck.io%2Fcrashes%2F1&d=eu0lilLN9Tjy39QEn%2BRyli%2B7EDXmwg1SXj7S5MqlT1o%3D&h=1ce3b788\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hkfactcheck.io/crashes/1</a><br />\n<br />\n誠邀：曾出席『<span style=\"color: red;\">民主歌聲獻中華</span>』演藝人、所有民主派議員、及候選人。〔民主派即是所有推動民主，包括本土及泛民〕<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">光復香港 時代革命</span><br />\n<br />\n11.24 民主歌聲獻香港 圍繞理大走一圈 【和理非行動post】<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1747254\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1747254</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">幫幫手推一推行動post拉！連登重有邊個唔去投票！</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n下期預告：12.1 民主歌聲撐林夕 圍繞理大走一圈 【行動post】"},{"pid":"320565b2bad4a91a00198e72cb86ba8fca383081","tid":1745234,"uid":78947,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T15:08:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"295cffedf1ae9b9b651a59613775e93fd6c18382","tid":1745234,"uid":235025,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T15:08:59.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"1599661fc6c4550f30f1e50c751859f02313b012","tid":1745234,"uid":82640,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b950eb760a3e53cefa9403f2864dc18916a28d1c","tid":1745234,"uid":8014,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T06:22:32.000Z","msg":"好多區2個黃1個藍<br />\n<br />\n隨時贏票輸議席."},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T15:09:25.000Z","msg":"基本目標就係總票數要超過帝制派"},{"pid":"20cd8ffac66d0b38112b8018bf09baab7880a69f","tid":1745234,"uid":262125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b950eb760a3e53cefa9403f2864dc18916a28d1c","tid":1745234,"uid":8014,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T06:22:32.000Z","msg":"好多區2個黃1個藍<br />\n<br />\n隨時贏票輸議